title: Ebro In The Morning - "You Never Even Met Her!"
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 9/8.

Ebro and the crew discuss the passing of Mac Miller, Drake on Monday Night Football, and much more. Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (6, 47, and 1:04) and you find out who played themselves.
